    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294890/extras/14be9b76262daea3f5009861a4f5bd9b.avif?t=1760456258\" width=600 height=172 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BLUNDERBUSTED</strong> is the world's first roguelike lightgun shooter. Arcade style quick play with strategic powerups, interactive stages, and tons of action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294890/extras/19f9202be823de18990f3281b829a561.poster.avif?t=1760456258\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294890/extras/19f9202be823de18990f3281b829a561.webm?t=1760456258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294890/extras/19f9202be823de18990f3281b829a561.mp4?t=1760456258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >EARLY ACCESS FEATURES</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic gun powerup system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic arcade style action with quick play sessions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Massive replayability with new gear unlocks for varied playstyles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Surprising stage interactibles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Target practice range for relaxing, calibrating, and testing weapons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support for all major light guns (Blamcon, Sinden, Gun4IR, Ultimarc, etc.)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >UPCOMING FEATURES</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional environments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional enemy types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Score attack challenges</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More interactibles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online leaderboards</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the Dark Tonic Games Discord Community</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294890/extras/4220c1b4ed248902b657187f2cd99b41.poster.avif?t=1760456258\" width=616 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294890/extras/4220c1b4ed248902b657187f2cd99b41.webm?t=1760456258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294890/extras/4220c1b4ed248902b657187f2cd99b41.mp4?t=1760456258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help shape what Blunderbusted will become! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294890/extras/75e5b0e79b47b8027d77a483cedd0507.avif?t=1760456258\" width=600 height=88 /></span></p>",
